The paper deals with the problem of detecting fake images and videos, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. It also involves the use of deep learning algorithms, which are commonly used in the computer security (cs.CR) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the use of capsule networks, which is a relatively new and emerging area of research in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
